# ─── LaTeX ISA guidebook build artefacts ─────────────────────────
# main.tex (and any future *.tex at the repo root) produces a heavy
# debris trail on every xelatex pass.  The .tex source itself is
# tracked; only the generated intermediate files are ignored.  The
# published PDF lives at _static/downloads/pccx-isa-v002.pdf and IS
# tracked so the Furo site can serve it directly without a CI round-
# trip.
*.aux
*.log
*.out
*.toc
*.lof
*.lot
*.fls
*.fdb_latexmk
*.synctex.gz
*.synctex
*.bcf
*.run.xml
*.blg
*.bbl
*.nav
*.snm
*.vrb
*.idx
*.ilg
*.ind
*.xdv
*.dvi
*.ps
*.tex.bak

# Root-level PDF is a build artefact — the tracked copy is under
# _static/downloads/ only.
/main.pdf

# MiKTeX / TeX Live scratch directories
auxiliary/
/latex.out/

